</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA032" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-704C0C6B-5CA9-4D4D-B8A9-6C1132D65581.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the cover below the cover of the knife...?>24 How to remove the cover below the cover of the knife compartment</xref> 
