</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the media input right cover. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA022" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A1586343-23C1-47B2-BE4B-BB8972057671.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the media input right cover?>24 How to remove the media input right cover</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA012" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-1C874C66-3A17-4AC4-886B-753A1A37D196.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 Open the ink system (todo)?>02 Open the ink system</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the rear top cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="02DISA014" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-44A21941-A21F-4C37-A066-3CEA7BE54DAA.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system...?>02 How to remove the rear top cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the lower cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA052" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-3EA4F7FC-3249-452F-A681-38FC94D794B9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the lower cover of the ink system?>24 How to remove the lower cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the top cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA056" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0EC7B866-5C12-4DD8-B785-606D4BE4F19B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the top cover of the ink system?>24 How to remove the top cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the middle cover of the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA054" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-3DDBA7E4-FC98-4D59-B862-147D49213A2E.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the middle cover of the ink system?>24 How to remove the middle cover of the ink system</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close (= rotate to horizontal position) the 2 valves of the printheads (1... 6). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-5980C93E-C709-4969-AB48-46B240E28CAA" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-4A5A1449-D301-4B71-A22D-D3D018337247-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4A5A1449-D301-4B71-A22D-D3D018337247-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="SECTION_4AAEB624BD5D4C1FBE4191BD422BB53F" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-A85C321B-F308-43E0-934E-A3E1E02ABCC6" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Do 
<xref keyref="02DISA009" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0DEE531B-1829-44B1-9D7D-2489745F722D.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the ink refill unit?>02 How to remove the ink refill unit</xref> for this color. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7F0E054A-9A39-4793-B568-E658D1D26544" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B86D8410-36A2-495E-98D2-7734E2E5649F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B86D8410-36A2-495E-98D2-7734E2E5649F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the connector of stirring motor. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7DB43840-76D1-4C65-80BE-EEA30827357F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0CCEBAF9-FECC-4EED-B828-DD4F270907D3-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0CCEBAF9-FECC-4EED-B828-DD4F270907D3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the cover of the ink pump. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the ink pump tube. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-37B4B8AE-45F1-4992-B72F-A34CEFBB9FDD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C2C5750B-F933-46B5-939A-B14024DD198C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C2C5750B-F933-46B5-939A-B14024DD198C-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-0FA15BAA-B3E5-47E2-ACE2-DA145530370C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F6916527-F5A2-4ADD-978A-ADF5766BF6B4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F6916527-F5A2-4ADD-978A-ADF5766BF6B4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screw of the bracket of the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FF081033-FC63-4D0E-B1AD-BD9553ED96BB" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E7F39FB-DAF1-4DE3-854A-84F6590CBEE1-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E7F39FB-DAF1-4DE3-854A-84F6590CBEE1-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift and remove the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-3BAC12E3-99DC-4B7E-85F5-ECFA333F674F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C1CB31DD-8EEB-40A8-A7C2-579BDD406176-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C1CB31DD-8EEB-40A8-A7C2-579BDD406176-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift and remove the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6D783914-3660-4511-9404-D39CE59BD473" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-872A2DF4-539E-40A5-AE60-80C891C5A8E9-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-872A2DF4-539E-40A5-AE60-80C891C5A8E9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the ink tank and motor to the top. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4EC0F96D-5FB8-4416-AD77-FD240E04CE57" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-491FAF8A-5305-4CA1-926F-66096202834C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-491FAF8A-5305-4CA1-926F-66096202834C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place a new maintenance tray in front of the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the top cover of the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-3EC3F176-A734-43C4-A39A-28FF04556B80" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-3DEEDD76-4F7E-4949-A0C5-3D008FFD688A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3DEEDD76-4F7E-4949-A0C5-3D008FFD688A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Hold the ink tank and slide out carefully the mixer blade. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-084C866B-0F8C-4F2F-A950-A43AB1C3FE9F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F2D4C3A0-219B-4D36-B415-16906312ED7D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F2D4C3A0-219B-4D36-B415-16906312ED7D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the mixer blade in the maintenance tray. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E44495C0-7186-4A4A-8CF7-3D53559BA3C7" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-27B3BFE8-7C57-49A9-AAE3-94F0BF91F33B-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-27B3BFE8-7C57-49A9-AAE3-94F0BF91F33B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fill the new ink tank with the ink of the old ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the mixer in the ink tank and lock the top cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F3DB5423-542F-460F-B632-6804368AAA92" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-43324D7F-2676-48F0-A28A-9666F65E128E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-43324D7F-2676-48F0-A28A-9666F65E128E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the ink tank (flat surface of the ink tank at the sensors side) in the unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the refill unit. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-B7B9F502-5ED9-4713-9375-6D16E474A718" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure the funnel is in the top cover of the ink tank. 
</p></note><p class="- topic/p ">See 
<xref keyref="02DISA009" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0DEE531B-1829-44B1-9D7D-2489745F722D.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 How to remove the ink refill unit?>02 How to remove the ink refill unit</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the bracket of the ink tank. 
